{
  "stem": "7238.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because this was not the food for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had to work in the basement to peel potatoes that often we stole the few potatoes to take them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And 25 people who-- who belonged to the underground, we got into one big room, slept on the floor, and waited what will happen next.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was in January.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And news from the front came that it's almost over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Until May '45, we knew this is the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And now, with great hopes, I waited for my husband and for my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It took a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And to kill my sorrow and to grow according to my profession, I opened up a little school in this room where we lived for those youngsters who survived, who came out from bunkers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I worked with them until June '45.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Then I decided to go and look for my family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- the trains didn't run properly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "There was only one train going through the-- through the border of Czechoslovakia, Poland and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And everybody had to present a document.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We had only from the Jewish counsel a document written in Polish that we are-- that we are going to look for our families.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "This was the document.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And people packed into the trains until the Russian general came and asked for our documents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He couldn't read it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he went to his office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the train left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here I am with my friend, standing on the trucks and asking, what next?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A Polish worker came over to us both.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what did we have?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In our knapsack, we had two loaves of bread and one carton of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
